          "cookie": [],
          "body": "---\nopenapi: 3.1.0\ncomponents:\n  schemas:\n    APIResponseDTOListProductDTO:\n      type: object\n      properties:\n        grpcCode:\n          type: string\n        message:\n          type: string\n        data:\n          type: array\n          items:\n            $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ProductDTO\"\n    APIResponseDTOProductDTO:\n      type: object\n      properties:\n        grpcCode:\n          type: string\n        message:\n          type: string\n        data:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/ProductDTO\"\n    APIResponseDTOVoid:\n      type: object\n      properties:\n        grpcCode:\n          type: string\n        message:\n          type: string\n        data: {}\n    CreateProductDTO:\n      type: object\n      required:\n        - name\n        - price\n        - description\n        - quantity\n        - tags\n      properties:\n        name:\n          type: string\n          pattern: \\S\n        price:\n          type: number\n          format: double\n          exclusiveMinimum: 0\n        description:\n          type: string\n          pattern: \\S\n        quantity:\n          type: integer\n          format: int32\n          minimum: 0\n        tags:\n          type: string\n          pattern: \\S\n    LocalDateTime:\n      type: string\n      format: date-time\n      examples:\n        - 2022-03-10T12:15:50\n    ProductDTO:\n      type: object\n      properties:\n        id:\n          type: string\n        name:\n          type: string\n        price:\n          type: number\n          format: double\n        description:\n          type: string\n        quantity:\n          type: integer\n          format: int32\n        creationDate:\n          $ref: \"#/components/schemas/LocalDateTime\"\n        tags:\n          type: string\n        active:\n          type: boolean\n    UpdateProductDTO:\n      type: object\n      required:\n        - name\n        - price\n        - description\n        - quantity\n        - tags\n        - active\n      properties:\n        name:\n          type: string\n          pattern: \\S\n        price:\n          type: number\n          format: double\n          exclusiveMinimum: 0\n        description:\n          type: string\n          pattern: \\S\n        quantity:\n          type: integer\n          format: int32\n          minimum: 0\n        tags:\n          type: string\n          pattern: \\S\n        active:\n          type: boolean\npaths:\n  /amadeus/api/v1/products:\n    get:\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: OK\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/APIResponseDTOListProductDTO\"\n      summary: Get All Products\n      tags:\n        - Product Resource\n    post:\n      requestBody:\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/CreateProductDTO\"\n        required: true\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: OK\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/APIResponseDTOProductDTO\"\n        \"400\":\n          description: Bad Request\n      summary: Create Product\n      tags:\n        - Product Resource\n  /amadeus/api/v1/products/{id}:\n    put:\n      parameters:\n        - name: id\n          in: path\n          required: true\n          schema:\n            type: string\n            pattern: \\S\n      requestBody:\n        content:\n          application/json:\n            schema:\n              $ref: \"#/components/schemas/UpdateProductDTO\"\n        required: true\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: OK\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/APIResponseDTOProductDTO\"\n        \"400\":\n          description: Bad Request\n      summary: Update Product\n      tags:\n        - Product Resource\n    get:\n      parameters:\n        - name: id\n          in: path\n          required: true\n          schema:\n            type: string\n            pattern: \\S\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: OK\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/APIResponseDTOProductDTO\"\n      summary: Get Product By Id\n      tags:\n        - Product Resource\n    delete:\n      parameters:\n        - name: id\n          in: path\n          required: true\n          schema:\n            type: string\n            pattern: \\S\n      responses:\n        \"200\":\n          description: OK\n          content:\n            application/json:\n              schema:\n                $ref: \"#/components/schemas/APIResponseDTOVoid\"\n      summary: Delete Product\n      tags:\n        - Product Resource\ninfo:\n  title: rest-service API\n  version: 1.0.0-SNAPSHOT\n"
